parameters:
Pawnshop Flea Market: I'm sorry, I had to leave in the
middle.

Pawnshop Flea Market: How is your son actually doing? Does
he have the talent to become a magician?
Magician Relm: Well, as for me--
Young Carti: Huff, huff, do I not have any talent?

Young Carti: 'Anato-sensei said that I should find a path
other than being a magician.'
Pawnshop Flea Market: Relm-san, is that really true...?
Magician Relm: That might be true for now.

Young Carti: Is that so, I am not cut out to be a
magician...

Magician Relm: That's just for now! If there's a situation
where my talent blossoms, it might change.

Young Carti: Please tell me specifically! I absolutely,
absolutely want to become a magician!

Magician Relm: ......Not only me, but my friends have also
grown significantly through dragon subjugation.

Magician Relm: Dragons may no longer exist, but it is
important to have the mindset of taking on big challenges.

Young Carti: I understand, Lady Relm! I will definitely take
on big challenges, I promise!
Magician Relm: Lady Relm... that's too exaggerated.
Young Carti: Dad, I want to study, so let's go back quickly!

Pawnshop Flea Market: This will be the reward for this time,
thank you very much, Sensei.

Pawnshop Flea Market: If you'd like, please come and visit
again.
Magician Relm (Irresponsible words... I understand that)
Magician Relm (But, if you can give up, it's not a dream)
